snippet.title: Sploot Trailer
snippet.description:
Download for free here!
http://edgeofprophecy.itch.io/sploot

Experience life as a Seagull!

Fly around a scenic island town!

Poop on everything!

The premier VR seagull experience. Built for the Oculus Rift, but playable without one.
